spec_data.Name: tomcat-jsvc
spec_data.Description:
Systemd service to start tomcat with jsvc,
which allows tomcat to perform some privileged operations
(e.g. bind to a port < 1024) and then switch identity to a non-privileged user.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 21 Aug 2017 11:34:10 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Apache jsvc wrapper for Apache Tomcat as separate service
